{"tid":168821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人生自古有咩意義？","createTime":"2017-03-23T20:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T20:19:09.000Z","uid":94031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db9da293370c018d56bd6b9e52341155a0ab9f0c","tid":168821,"uid":94031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T20:04:19.000Z","msg":"追完幼稚園日記果個作者的漫畫，<br />\n再一次覺得人生好辛苦，冇乜希望<br />\n個作者都幾有深度既痴線佬<br />\n<br />\n晚晚都慣左亂諗野<br />\n<br />\n做人好煩 點解要做人 <br />\n唔會亂黎 但都想9up一句想死"},{"pid":"f7cbb63e816881502570d510c0b7e01e8f5e8d53","tid":168821,"uid":42621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T20:08:15.000Z","msg":"我都追左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過又唔使咁灰 就算真你比你搵到個意義 你都未必會想跟住黎做 咁倒不如追求自己希望想做既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba15313922c0bbf7155b40bdfbbcc910ee0bf5c8","tid":168821,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T20:10:36.000Z","msg":"為咗享樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0548fc2eb6ae6358d5418f0176758d3c4bfa517","tid":168821,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T20:11:16.000Z","msg":"去下旅行 透下新鮮空氣 放鬆下心情<br />\n有助你思考人生既意義 發現其實相比其他動物做人幸福好多自由好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2310421165b0795f091aab07050ecd6881af023d","tid":168821,"uid":94031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T20:19:09.000Z","msg":"點解做人一定要搞掂好自己先會遇到一個人同自己一齊行？點解一定要我做好自己先？點解唔可以有人救我帶領我？點解要人救就係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好明白要做好自己先可以吸引好的人<br />\n但點解好既人唔可以救左我先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}